---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout 
  title="Case Studies" 
  description="Real-world success stories from companies using Cogintech AI"
>
  <div class="space-y-16">
    <section class="text-center">
      <p class="text-lg text-foreground/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        See how leading oil & gas companies are transforming their equipment integrity analysis 
        with Cogintech AI, achieving significant cost savings and faster report delivery.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-12">
      <article class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-border shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cogintech-blue to-cogintech-teal p-8 text-white">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold">M</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Major Offshore Operator</h2>
              <p class="text-white/80">Gulf of Mexico Operations</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-cogintech-blue mb-2">35%</div>
              <div class="text-foreground/80">Cost Reduction</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-cogintech-teal mb-2">18 hours</div>
              <div class="text-foreground/80">Report Delivery</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-cogintech-orange mb-2">97.2%</div>
              <div class="text-foreground/80">Accuracy Rate</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-cogintech-blue">Challenge</h3>
              <p class="text-foreground/80">
                This major offshore operator was struggling with lengthy inspection analysis cycles taking 45-60 days, 
                causing delays in critical maintenance decisions. High expert labor costs and inconsistent report quality 
                across different inspection teams were major concerns.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-cogintech-blue">Solution</h3>
              <p class="text-foreground/80 mb-4">
                Implemented Cogintech's multi-agent AI system to analyze inspection data from 150+ offshore platforms. 
                The system processes historical inspection records and generates comprehensive integrity analysis reports.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-foreground/80">
                <li>• Automated data ingestion from multiple inspection sources</li>
                <li>• AI-powered analysis with multi-agent verification</li>
                <li>• Standardized reporting format across all platforms</li>
                <li>• Integration with existing maintenance planning systems</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-cogintech-blue">Results</h3>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-700 mb-2">Financial Impact</h4>
                  <ul class="text-sm text-green-600 space-y-1">
                    <li>• $2.1M annual savings in analysis costs</li>
                    <li>• 60% reduction in expert review time</li>
                    <li>• Faster maintenance scheduling</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-blue-200">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-2">Operational Impact</h4>
                  <ul class="text-sm text-blue-600 space-y-1">
                    <li>• 18-hour average report delivery</li>
                    <li>• 97.2% accuracy validated by experts</li>
                    <li>• Improved maintenance planning efficiency</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-border shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cogintech-teal to-cogintech-orange p-8 text-white">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold">R</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Regional Pipeline Company</h2>
              <p class="text-white/80">North American Pipeline Network</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-cogintech-blue mb-2">42%</div>
              <div class="text-foreground/80">Cost Reduction</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-cogintech-teal mb-2">24 hours</div>
              <div class="text-foreground/80">Critical Findings</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-cogintech-orange mb-2">95.8%</div>
              <div class="text-foreground/80">Accuracy Rate</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-cogintech-blue">Challenge</h3>
              <p class="text-foreground/80">
                Managing integrity analysis for 3,000+ miles of pipeline with limited expert resources. 
                Traditional analysis was taking 30-45 days, creating bottlenecks in maintenance scheduling 
                and regulatory compliance reporting.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-cogintech-blue">Solution</h3>
              <p class="text-foreground/80 mb-4">
                Deployed Cogintech AI across the entire pipeline network with prioritized analysis for critical segments. 
                The system integrates with ILI (In-Line Inspection) data and external inspection reports.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-foreground/80">
                <li>• Automated processing of ILI and external inspection data</li>
                <li>• Risk-based prioritization of analysis</li>
                <li>• Natural language querying for historical data</li>
                <li>• Regulatory compliance reporting automation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-cogintech-blue">Results</h3>
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cogintech-blue/5 to-cogintech-teal/5 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3">Key Achievements</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-foreground/80">
                      <li>• 42% reduction in analysis costs</li>
                      <li>• Critical findings delivered in 24 hours</li>
                      <li>• 100% on-time regulatory reporting</li>
                      <li>• Improved maintenance planning accuracy</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3">Business Value</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-foreground/80">
                      <li>• $1.8M annual cost savings</li>
                      <li>• 75% faster decision-making</li>
                      <li>• Enhanced regulatory compliance</li>
                      <li>• Reduced expert resource requirements</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-border shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cogintech-orange to-cogintech-blue p-8 text-white">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold">I</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Independent Inspection Services</h2>
              <p class="text-white/80">Multi-Client Service Provider</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-cogintech-blue mb-2">3x</div>
              <div class="text-foreground/80">Capacity Increase</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-cogintech-teal mb-2">12 hours</div>
              <div class="text-foreground/80">Average Delivery</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-cogintech-orange mb-2">98.5%</div>
              <div class="text-foreground/80">Client Satisfaction</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-cogintech-blue">Challenge</h3>
              <p class="text-foreground/80">
                An independent inspection services company needed to scale their analysis capabilities 
                to serve more clients without proportionally increasing expert staff. Quality consistency 
                across different analysts was also a concern.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-cogintech-blue">Solution</h3>
              <p class="text-foreground/80 mb-4">
                Integrated Cogintech AI as a force multiplier for their expert analysts, handling initial 
                analysis and flagging areas requiring human attention. The system maintains quality 
                consistency across all client reports.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-cogintech-blue">Impact</h3>
              <p class="text-foreground/80">
                Tripled their analysis capacity while maintaining the same expert headcount. 
                Improved client satisfaction with faster delivery times and consistent report quality. 
                The company now serves as a preferred partner for major operators seeking rapid, 
                reliable integrity analysis.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-cogintech-dark text-white p-12 rounded-lg text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Join These Success Stories?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        See how Cogintech AI can transform your equipment integrity analysis process. 
        Schedule a personalized demo with your actual inspection data.
      </p>
      <a 
        href="/#lead-form" 
        class="inline-block bg-cogintech-orange hover:bg-cogintech-orange/90 text-white font-medium px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition-colors text-lg"
      >
        Request Your Demo
      </a>
    </section>
  </div>
</PageLayout>